OL,3,CTranslink workers vote to reject pay
OL,4,Coffer
OL,6,FPublic transport workers in Northern
OL,7,FIreland have rejected what unions have
OL,8,Fcalled an "inadequate pay increase
OL,9,Ffrom Translink".
OL,11,FIn a joint statement, Unite, GMB and
OL,12,FSIPTU confirmed their members had
OL,13,Foverwhelmingly rejected a pay increase
OL,14,Fof five percent plus a one-off payment
OL,15,Fof #1,500 for the 2023-24 financial
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,18,FBus and rail workers voted with
OL,19,Fmajorities of approximately 70 per
OL,20,Fcent to reject the pay offer.
